snippet.title: Tales of Wind Trailer - Ahri always by your side
snippet.description:
The most heartwarming mobile game of 2019
https://tow.neocraftstudio.com/
Explore a vast open world with your friends. Show your skills in PVP Arena. Most importantly, meet your destined romance in your adventure! Pre-register NOW!
Tales of wind will globally launch at end of April in North America, Europe, South America, and Oceania! 7 language options are fully supported including English, Spanish, French, German, Portuguese, Russian and Turkish!
Don't hesistate to pre-register now! See you then! Click here to pre-register Now!
